# Methods 

* buildIndex.sh script is to build a salmon index from the de-novo transcriptome 
* alignAll.sh script is to align the Aip samples according to the Aipindex using Salmon 
* mergeKo.R script will merge the aligned transcripts to their genes 
* de.R script is to import the Salmon alignments into DESeq2 and perfrom differential expression analysis, and also splitting them on the basis of their padg value
